	   <tr><td colspan=2>Our party of gnomes was attacked and mostly destroyed by this fellow due to bad faction.  <br>Level 10 - 12 characters CANNOT take this guy.<br><br>Our warrior did the Bullsmasher quest 25 times until he got the mace.  As a result ALL the clockworks hate him, including Nilits!<br><br>So even though we hadn't bothered him, Nilits joined in a fight we were having with two other clockworks.    He hits hard and fast and can stun. He killed the warrior, the cleric (me) when I tried to heal the warrior, and the wizzie that hit him with a spell.<br><br>On the plus side after slaughtering us he walked off and ignored the rogue in our party.  So its possible that if you have ok faction, and DON"T annoy him, he might leave you alone.  (or maybe the rogue just managed to hide....)      <br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
