	   <tr><td colspan=2>At 22, every Nilit's Clockwork I've seen has been high blue so I would say the level range is slightly lower than that given.  The Gnome Tinkered Toy is for a quest in Kerra Isle.  Give this toy to the Kerran children and they will give you their old toy, an AC3 AGI+2 range slot item, in return.  I'm not sure exactly how fast they spawn but it seems to be fairly quickly.  When I went hunting them, I found 2.  I killed one while someone else killed the other.  By the time I'd gotten my mana back, a third had spawned.  If you're having trouble finding one, just kill the rogue clockworks around the minotaur caves as those seem to be the placeholders.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
